00:39:51,580 --> 00:39:53,460
We gave him 1,500 units

641
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:54,460
on the day of surgery.

642
00:39:54,780 --> 00:39:56,620
And then we gave him
daily intravenous antibiotics.

